-- News Corp sees plenty of growth in German pay-TV
-- 
-- Mon Jan 7, 2008 1:14pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/01/07/us-premiere-unitymedia-newscorp-ceo-idUSWEB143920080107

 

 FRANKFURT  (Reuters) - News Corp's NWSa.N chief executive said it had decided to buy a stake in Germany's pay-TV broadcaster Premiere PREGn.DE because it saw large growth potential in the country's pay-TV market. 

 "We see enormous potential for growth in Germany and believe the time is right to invest in its foremost pay-TV business, Premiere," News Corp Chief Executive Rupert Murdoch said in a statement on Monday. (Reporting by  Nicola Leske )